rComments: I am in the class right now so I can't speak to her level of difficulty. HOWEVER, she rushes through the course material so quickly. It is extremely hard to keep up when she speaks that fast. She cares more about getting through all the material than making sure the students understand it. Barely gives the class a 2 minute break. Wouldnt take again
A mediocre prof...lectures are  boring and repetitive. Her book/film choices are not all that great either. Marking-wise, she's pretty fair.
okay prof...easy marker, but really moody and she can be very rude to students!

She loves making everyone in the class read like 90% of the time, gets very very very tedious at times. Somewhat interesting, but kinda rare. Overall decent marker. I slept pretty often in the class and the tutorials were more helpful than the lectures themselves.

She's a solid prof .. great approach to lectures ... very clear and sound speaker with a lot of energy.  At times, she appeared to get a little arrogant because she knew she had our attention, but hey, she's American, so I understand.  Overall, she was probably my top prof this semster, although that may not be saying much.
she's a very good prof. she makes the class really interesting.. there's a lott of reading in class but she definitely helps u understand it.
